{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"deb2d2c6de","title":"在中央工作会议上的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ef3bffc8c6","index":0,"year":1964,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"deb2d2c6de"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4665c9bfba","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共工作会额上陈伯达回志发言时的插斋","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"14e971faf3","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年十二月二十七日）（注：方括号内为陈值达同志发言的有关内容）","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"43ceccc51d","type":"paragraph","text":"[主要矛盾是什么？主席根据大家的意见作了总结。主要矛盾是社会主义和资本主义的矛盾。四清与四不清不能说明问题的性质。封建社会就是清官与负官的问题。《四进士》就是反货官的！了","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"8ef10cc25a","type":"paragraph","text":"巡抚出朝，地动山播，可了不起理！","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"5433020527","type":"paragraph","text":"[封建时代的清官实质上是假的。“三年清知府，十万雪花银。”清，在不同社会有不同的阶级内容。资本主义社会也有所谓清官，那些清官都是大财阀。了","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"f922aed3f8","type":"paragraph","text":"清朝刘露的《老残游记》中说，清官害人，比资官害人还厉害。后来一查，南北朝史中的《魏史》就有此说。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"a46269fb3e","type":"paragraph","text":"[内部矛盾那个时代没有？党内党外矛盾交叉，党内有党。国民党也有此问题。了我们党内至少有两派，一个是社会主义派，一个是资本主义派。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"2e4f6fee40","type":"paragraph","text":"【主席强调，要听各方面的。好，坏，特别是反对的，要耐心听。这是工作做的好坏的准则。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"d802d58097","type":"paragraph","text":"讲长了怎么办？李雪拳同志说的，讲长了打零分。讲长了，让他讲长！横直没人听嘛！","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"bfe1e5fb2d","type":"paragraph","text":"[许多人忘记自己是从那里来的。不能忘本嘛！我这个人不参加革命，顶多是个小学教员、中学教员而已。】","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"83f6a27f7a","type":"paragraph","text":"大宜是从小官来的，小管是从老百姓来的。我们都是从老百姓中来的，还是老百姓赚！“蒋委员长”不姓蒋，姓郑，叫郑三发子，河南人氏，只知有母，不知有父，还不是老百姓变的？","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"ac6bd8177a","type":"paragraph","text":"[主席常说，不要自以为是。多干部当权，就以为自己的意见对。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"c7e81c82d7","type":"paragraph","text":"不要当了权，就是自己的意见对。自以为是，没有自以为不是的。为什么要开会？就是意见不一致。一致了开会干什么","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"631c95b585","type":"paragraph","text":"[不怕官，只怕管！】小官怕大宜，大官怕洋人。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"ccf3e50578","type":"paragraph","text":"在中央工作会上的","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"c5fb1ea584","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六四年十二月二十八日）没有多的讲。这个文件（指二十三条）行不行？第一条，性质问题，这样规定可不可以？有三种提法，前两种较好？还是第三种较好","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"},{"id":"3221d61ac4","type":"paragraph","text":"·199","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de"}],"page":{"id":"30ce429f6e","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"deb2d2c6de","start":212,"end":212}}}},"__N_SSG":true}